====== H6862: צַר ======

===== Source =====

or   ; from  H6887 ;

===== Meaning =====

narrow ; (as a noun) a  tight  place (usually figuratively, i.e.  trouble ); also a  pebble  (as in  H6864 ); (transitive) an  opponent  (as  crowding )

===== Definitions =====

  - narrow
  - tight
  - trouble
  - pebble
  - opponent
  - crowding

===== Usage =====

adversary, afflicted(-tion), anguish, close, distress, enemy, flint, foe, narrow, small, sorrow, strait, tribulation, trouble.
